channel.title: Problem loading private servers?
channel.description:
I have been trying out a bunch of private servers, but every single time it just says "Sorry, an error has occurred whilst loading Runescape." It was working fine but then after old school online crashed while i was playing it hasn't worked.
P.S. I am using an iMac
